{"tid":1539122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔需要解散警隊, 但需要立法解除警察武裝","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:05:26.000Z","uid":280152,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05c784bd8a55563d6881a0db778346a4ea77e604","tid":1539122,"uid":280152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"1.希望佢地永遠做警察服務市民<br />\n2.警察成日話自己為市民服務, 維持法紀, 咁佢地冇gear 都一樣可以繼續實踐理想<br />\n3.政府經常話警察係使用最低武力, 解除武裝, 赤手空拳先能夠確保警察使用最低武力<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議立法禁止警察使用任何類型槍械,任何類型武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b3546f9fbea184da1e2dc7c08ccf802db6f3ef","tid":1539122,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a95526812bf397c9cc9fbf88665c826f03472dd","tid":1539122,"uid":